        "content": "<p>well you can just set <code>setext</code> to be <code>apply set.ext; intro x</code></p>",
        "id": 125155166,
        "sender_full_name": "Kenny Lau",
        "timestamp": 1523895341
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I want <code>x</code> to be an argument of the tactic</p>",
        "id": 125155173,
